==Description==
The '''Heart Scale''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Heart Scale has a value of 10 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Heart Scale appears in the Underground as a 2x2 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:HeartScaleMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Heart Scales can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], as [[Rare Hold Items]] from [[File:Luvdisc.png|30px]] Luvdisc, and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

